<template><AdminTablePage title="招聘会管理" desc="发布大型招聘会、专场招聘会及参会统计" :list="list" :total="total" :loading="loading" :query="query" @load="load" @open="open"><template #columns><el-table-column prop="title" label="招聘会" min-width="190"/><el-table-column prop="fairTime" label="时间" width="180"/><el-table-column prop="location" label="地点" min-width="150"/><el-table-column prop="host" label="主办方" min-width="150"/><el-table-column prop="companyCount" label="企业数" width="90"/><el-table-column prop="jobCount" label="岗位数" width="90"/><el-table-column prop="signCount" label="报名" width="80"/></template><template #rowActions="{row}"><el-button text type="primary" @click="open(row)">编辑</el-button><el-button text type="danger" @click="del(row)">删除</el-button></template><template #dialogs><el-dialog v-model="dialog" title="招聘会" width="680px"><el-form :model="form" label-width="90px"><el-form-item label="标题"><el-input v-model="form.title"/></el-form-item><el-form-item label="时间"><el-date-picker v-model="form.fairTime" type="datetime" value-format="YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss" style="width:100%"/></el-form-item><el-form-item label="地点"><el-input v-model="form.location"/></el-form-item><el-form-item label="主办方"><el-input v-model="form.host"/></el-form-item><el-form-item label="内容"><el-input v-model="form.content" type="textarea" :rows="4"/></el-form-item></el-form><template #footer><el-button @click="dialog=false">取消</el-button><el-button type="primary" @click="save">保存</el-button></template></el-dialog></template></AdminTablePage></template><script setup>import{reactive,ref,onMounted}from'vue';import{ElMessage,ElMessageBox}from'element-plus';import AdminTablePage from '@/components/AdminTablePage.vue';import{adminApi}from'@/api';const query=reactive({pageNum:1,pageSize:10,title:''});const list=ref([]),total=ref(0),loading=ref(false),dialog=ref(false),form=reactive({});const load=async()=>{loading.value=true;try{const r=await adminApi.fairs(query);list.value=r.data.records;total.value=Number(r.data.total)}finally{loading.value=false}};const open=row=>{Object.keys(form).forEach(k=>delete form[k]);Object.assign(form,row||{status:1,companyCount:0,jobCount:0,signCount:0});dialog.value=true};const save=async()=>{await adminApi.saveFair(form);ElMessage.success('保存成功');dialog.value=false;load()};const del=row=>ElMessageBox.confirm('确定删除该招聘会？').then(async()=>{await adminApi.delFair(row.id);load()});onMounted(load)</script>